description: Testing standards and coverage requirements
globs: **/*.{test,spec}.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: true
---

# Testing Pyramid
- Unit tests: 70% — pure functions, utilities, hooks
- Integration tests: 20% — component + API interaction
- E2E tests: 10% — critical user flows only

# Rules
- Every bug fix gets a regression test FIRST
- Test behavior, not implementation (black box testing)
- Use React Testing Library — query by role, label, text (not test-id)
- Mock external services, test error states and loading states
- Coverage threshold: 80% branches, 70% lines minimum

# Test Structure (AAA Pattern)
- Arrange: Set up data and mocks
- Act: Execute the function/interaction
- Assert: Check the expected outcome

# E2E (Playwright/Cypress)
- Test happy path + 2-3 error paths per flow
- Use data-testid ONLY for E2E selectors
- Run against production-like data in CI
- Screenshots on failure for debugging
